song_name: The Ballad Of The Costa Concordia
version_description: This is a transcription of the studio version to one guitar part. In addition to the chords, it contains two tablature sections that detail the third verse introduction and the outro keyboard arpeggios.

Note: Will sometimes messes around with the highest finger on the Am and D chords near the end of a measure, and adds in a D7 chord in some of the repetitions at the end, If you listen to the song you'll get it pretty easily. You can do this to your taste and it will sound fine.
